30#include "soft-fp.h"
31#include "extended.h"
32#include "quad.h"
33
34XFtype
35__trunctfxf2 (TFtype a)
36{
37 FP_DECL_EX;
38 FP_DECL_Q (A);
39 FP_DECL_E (R);
40 XFtype r;
41
42 FP_INIT_ROUNDMODE;
43 FP_UNPACK_SEMIRAW_Q (A, a);
44#if (2 * _FP_W_TYPE_SIZE) < _FP_FRACBITS_Q
45 FP_TRUNC (E, Q, 4, 4, R, A);
46#else
47 FP_TRUNC (E, Q, 2, 2, R, A);
48#endif
49 FP_PACK_SEMIRAW_E (r, R);
50 FP_HANDLE_EXCEPTIONS;
51
52 return r;
53}
